description: A Dubai Based Rent a car Company
overview:
Autorent is a leading car rental company based in the middle east, headquarted at Dubai, United Arab Emirates, having offices at Sultanate of Oman and Kingdom of Saudi Arabia.

The company has over 10000 vehicles, with in-house service center facilities. Recently the company operates it limousine services named as “Autorent Limousine Services” in the Dubai, providing services in UAE and Oman.

Autorent serves corporates with their leasing needs, and rent a car services to leisure travellers, and limousine services as per the customer needs. The Company operates with a philosophy of putting the “Customer First” as their slogan.
